OL,3,CSewage spills in Oxfordshire raised at
OL,4,Cfirst Prime Minister's Questions
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has promised a
OL,7,F"tougher regime" of regulation for
OL,8,Fwater companies after an Oxfordshire
OL,9,FMP raised concerns about sewage spills.
OL,11,FLiberal Democrat Calum Miller told the
OL,12,Fprime minister about the amount of
OL,13,Fsewage being pumped into the River
OL,14,FEvenlode in the village of Combe.
OL,16,FThames Water said it had "clear and
OL,17,Fdeliverable plans to upgrade" its
OL,18,FCharlbury and Finstock sewage
OL,19,Ftreatment works to "increase treatment
OL,20,Fcapacity and reduce the number of
OL,21,Fstorm discharges".
