OL,3,CSewage spills in Oxfordshire raised at
OL,4,Cfirst Prime Minister's Questions
OL,6,FMr Miller, the MP for Bicester and
OL,7,FWoodstock, told the House of Commons:
OL,8,F"At Combe, in my constituency, Thames
OL,9,FWater has pumped sewage into the River
OL,10,FEvenlode for over 2,600 hours in the
OL,11,Flast year".
OL,13,FMr Miller added: "Thames Water was
OL,14,Fallowed by (water regulator) Ofwat to
OL,15,Fwithdraw #7 billion in dividends, yet
OL,16,Fnow wants to jack up my constituents'
OL,17,Fbills.
