OL,3,CSewage spills in Oxfordshire raised at
OL,4,Cfirst Prime Minister's Questions
OL,6,F"I welcome the Water Bill in the
OL,7,FKing's Speech, but will the prime
OL,8,Fminister agree with my constituents
OL,9,Fand me that the system is broken, and
OL,10,Fwill he now commit to scrapping Ofwat
OL,11,Fand replacing it with a tougher
OL,12,Fregulator that will finally put people
OL,13,Fand planet ahead of water company
OL,14,Fprofits?"
OL,16,FIt was the first question of Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer's inaugural Prime Minister's
OL,18,FQuestion Time.
