OL,6,FIn response, Sir Keir said: "I thank
OL,7,Fhim for raising this important issue
OL,8,Fin relation to water and customers
OL,9,Fshould not pay the price for the
OL,10,Fmismanagement by water companies.
OL,12,F"And we've already announced immediate
OL,13,Fsteps to put one or two companies
OL,14,Funder a tougher regime. The minister
OL,15,Ffor water will meet the bosses of
OL,16,Ffailing companies to hold them to
OL,17,Faccount for their performance."
