OL,3,CSewage spills in Oxfordshire raised at
OL,4,Cfirst Prime Minister's Questions
OL,6,FA Thames Water spokesperson told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "While all storm discharges are
OL,8,Funacceptable, the sewage system was
OL,9,Fhistorically designed to work in this
OL,10,Fway, to prevent sewage backing up into
OL,11,Fpeople's homes.
OL,13,F"We know how much people enjoy and
OL,14,Fappreciate our rivers, and we are
OL,15,Fcommitted to seeing our waterways
OL,16,Fthrive, but we can't do it alone.
OL,17,FFarming, industry, road runoff,
OL,18,Fwildlife and increasingly extreme
OL,19,Fweather also play a role in river
OL,20,Fhealth.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
