OL,6,F"We have clear and deliverable plans
OL,7,Fto upgrade 250 of our sites across the
OL,8,Fregion, to increase treatment capacity
OL,9,Fand reduce the number of storm
OL,10,Fdischarges, including at our Charlbury
OL,11,Fand Finstock sewage treatment works.
OL,13,F"As infrastructure ages and demand on
OL,14,Fit increases more investment is needed
OL,15,Facross the entire sector That's why
OL,16,Fwe've asked for increased investment
OL,17,Fin the next regulatory cycle between
OL,18,F2025-2030.
